<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>اَلْمُسْتَحِقُّونَ لِلرُّبُع<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>مِنْ الْمُسْتَحِقِّينَ لِلرُّبُعِ الزَّوْج<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>شُرُوطُ اِسْتِحْقَاقِ الزَّوْجِ لِلرُّبْع<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>اِسْتِحْقَاقُ الزَّوْجِ لِلرُّبُعِ عِنْدَ وُجُودِ الْفَرْعِ الْوَارِثِ لِلْمَيِّت<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{وَلَكُمْ نِصْفُ مَا تَرَكَ أَزْوَاجُكُمْ إِنْ لَمْ يَكُنْ لَهُنَّ وَلَدٌ , فَإِنْ كَانَ لَهُنَّ وَلَدٌ فَلَكُمُ الرُّبُعُ مِمَّا تَرَكْنَ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [النساء/١٢]</p> </div>